The Aurora Kernel Project
=========================

* Still naive, still experimental.

This project is a fork from SouthWest. It designed for Redmi Note 7(lavender)
devices.

If you want to use this kernel, please use a RDP(Retrofit Dynamic Partitions)
ROM and your device's original kernel version is 4.19. If your device's
original version isn't 4.19, please find a k4.19 ROM and flash it.

This project is experimental forever. use at your own risk.

Enjoy it :)
